SUMMARY:Seattle's French Fest: A Celebration of French-Speaking Cultures
DTSTAMP:20260318T135146Z
DTSTART:20260322T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle Center Festál presents Seattle’s French Fest: A Celebra
	tion of French Speaking Cultures in partnership with France Education Nort
	hwest (FEN). The festival celebrates the diversity of traditions\, ideas\,
	 dialects\, and more that make up French-speaking cultures around the worl
	d. While France is often the most well-known French-speaking country for p
	eople in the U.S.\, there are many other countries and places all around t
	he world where French is spoken.\n\nhttps://www.seattlecenter.com/events/e
	vent-calendar/seattles-french-fest-a-celebration-of-french-speaking-cultur
	es\n\nFrom Seattle Center Events
URL:https://www.seattlecenter.com/events/event-calendar/seattles-french-fes
	t-a-celebration-of-french-speaking-cultures
LOCATION:Armory
