DESCRIPTION:Join us for Live Music Happy Hour with the Joe Casalini Trio. T
	he Casalini Trio has played happy hours at the Royal Room since 2019. They
	 play laid-back\, swinging versions of great tunes by Duke Ellington\, Bil
	ly Strayhorn\, Hoagie Carmichael\, Phillip Johnston\, and other great Amer
	ican songwriters of the last 100 years. The happy hour usually lasts about
	 an hour and a half. Good drinks\, good people\, good ambience\, and there
	’s never a cover charge\, although the band often encourages donations to 
	local food banks and other worthy causes.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/
