BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:q3ZMMjU6Z-akNLjpIzYL9
SUMMARY:Women of SU at North Helpline
DTSTAMP:20260318T135146Z
DTSTART:20260328T153000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join the Women of SU for a volunteer opportunity with North Hel
	pline! Volunteers will help to distribute food to local community members 
	and people experiencing homelessness at the food bank in Lake City.\n\n \n
	\nSaturday\, March 28\n\n8:30 a.m. to 11:15 a.m.\n\nNorth Helpline\, Lake 
	City location | 12736 33rd Ave NE Seattle\, WA 98125\n\n \n\nSpots are lim
	ited. Register ASAP to secure your spot. Children eight to 17 years old ar
	e welcome to volunteer but must be accompanied by an adult guardian.\n\n \
	n\nQuestions? Please contact Ellen Montanana\, '17\, at montanan14@gmail.c
