DESCRIPTION:Mimosas Cabaret serves up a fierce drag and burlesque brunch\, 
	at The Mountain Room\, featuring "Death Becomes They/Them"\, a parody mini
	-musical packed with camp\, glamour\, and laughs. Sip cocktails while the 
	stunning cast of Mimosas Cabaret deliver high energy performances inspired
	 by the cult classic! Equal parts fabulous and unhinged\, this brunch is y
	our excuse to drink early\, tip generously\, and live forever! Siempre Viv
	a!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/mimosas-cabaret-ft-dea
	th-becomes-they-them/17986303/2026-03-29T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
